# Compiler Configuration

The SecureEthUsdcSwapV3 contract was compiled and verified using the following configuration.

---

## Compiler

- Language: Solidity
- Version: v0.8.26
- EVM version: cancun

---

## Optimizer

- Enabled: true
- Runs: 200
- viaIR: true

---

## Build Input

The original Standard JSON Input used during verification was not preserved at deployment time.

The file located at:

build/compilerInput.json

is a reconstructed Standard JSON Input derived from:
- verified source code on BaseScan
- on-chain compiler settings

The resulting bytecode matches the deployed contract exactly.
